::'''Dennis:''' Greetings, esteemed guest. I'm Dennis, the lobby manager of this hotel.
::'''Dennis:''' It's a pleasure to meet you. How can I assist you today?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What services do you provide?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503030704-->
::'''Dennis:''' As the lobby manager, it's my responsibility to attend to the guests' needs and help them resolve their issues.
::'''Dennis:''' Since you are new here, I assume you are not familiar with the hotel. Please allow me to offer some suggestions.
::'''Dennis:''' If you need assistance with room-related services, please choose either the manual service at the receptionist desk or the self-service terminal in the lobby.
::'''Dennis:''' For questions about entering the dream, please feel free to ask Giovanna, the Chief Dream Nurse.
::'''Dennis:''' In case of disputes with other guests or hotel staff, please seek assistance from Coty, the Head of Security.
::'''Dennis:''' The public dreamphone in the lobby allows you to make a quick call to any "moment" without entering the Dreamscape.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Much obliged.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503030711-->
:::'''Dennis:''' You're welcome. I'm just doing my job.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} ...Could you go over it again?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503030713-->
:::'''Dennis:''' ...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_503030714-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503030714-->
::'''Dennis:''' If you need more details, please make good use of your Dreamscape Pass.
::'''Dennis:''' May you have fun and enjoy your stay in the City of Dreams.
